EN: In autumn, the sky is especially blue.

ZH: 秋季是收获的季节。
EN: Autumn is the season of harvest.

ZH: 每年的秋季都有美丽的月亮。
EN: Every autumn has a beautiful moon.

ZH: 在秋季，夜晚会变得凉爽。
EN: In autumn, the nights become cool.

ZH: 秋季是观赏落叶的好时节。
EN: Autumn is a good time to admire falling leaves.

ZH: 秋季的田野变得金黄。
EN: The fields in autumn turn golden.

ZH: 秋季是一年中最浪漫的季节。
EN: Autumn is the most romantic season of the year.

