EN: The evenings in autumn are very peaceful.

ZH: 秋季的天空洁净无云。
EN: The sky in autumn is clear and cloudless.

ZH: 秋季是欣赏彩叶的好时机。
EN: Autumn is a good time to admire colorful leaves.
